\sum \limits_{n = 2}^\infty \frac{1}{(n-1)n(n+1)} \space(a)
\sum \limits_{n = 2}^\infty \frac{1}{2(n-1)}-\frac{1}{n}+\frac{1}{2(n+1)}
(a)
\sum \limits_{k} u_{k}-u_{k+1}
\left(\frac 1{2(n-1)}-\frac 1{2n}\right)-\left(\frac 1{2n}-\frac 1{2(n+1)}\right)=
\frac 1{2n(n-1)}-\frac 1{2(n+1)n}=
\frac 1{(n-1)n(n+1)}
